        {
            "id": 6364690,
            "title": "記憶體族群大反攻 南亞科領軍多檔高掛漲停",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>隨著美股四大指數反彈，SanDisk、美光等記憶體股也回神，台廠南亞科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>) 昨日也釋出正向展望，在利多加持下，台股記憶體族群今 (5) 日強勢表態，由南亞科領軍漲停，帶動華邦電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>)、福懋科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8131:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8131\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8131-TW</a>)、旺宏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2337:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2337\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2337-TW</a>) 等同步亮燈，上演絕地大反攻。</p></section><p><template id=\"P:1\"></template></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>南亞科指出，受惠 AI 需求快速擴張與新增產能有限影響，DRAM 市場至 2027 年上半年將維持供不應求，也針對個別客戶進行議價，將分別依單月、單季逐步調漲，預期第一季價格將逐月上漲，第二季價格會進一步跳增 (Jump)，預期到年底價格都將是穩定向上。</p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>除了前段產能緊張，南亞科也跟旗下福懋科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8131:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8131\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8131-TW</a>) 緊密合作，正積極擴充記憶體後段封測產能，雙方合作也進一步延伸至客製化記憶體的堆疊領域，預期福懋科今年營運將有顯著成長。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>記憶體族群今日強勢反彈，除亮燈漲停個股外，包括宇瞻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8271:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8271\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8271-TW</a>)、威剛 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3260:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3260\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3260-TW</a>)、南茂 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8150:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8150\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8150-TW</a>)、創見 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2451:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2451\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2451-TW</a>)、華東 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8110:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8110\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8110-TW</a>) 等，漲幅都在半根停板以上。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
