        {
            "id": 6364735,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 聯友金屬-創(7610)大漲7.41%，報290元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>聯友金屬-創(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7610:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7610\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7610-TW</a>)05日12:26股價上漲20元，報290.0元，漲幅7.41%，成交373張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>聯友金屬-創(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7610:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7610\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7610-TW</a>)所屬產業為綠能環保，主要業務為鎢酸鈉與硫酸鈷。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌10.89%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌7.3%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-89 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-89 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6364735",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 12:26:13",
